		<div class="resource">
			<h3>
				<a href="http://www.w3.org/blog/International/2013/04/29/new-article-unicode-bidirectional-algorithm-basics/" title="Permanent link to full entry">New article: Unicode Bidirectional Algorithm basics</a>
			</h3>
			<div class="description"> 
				<p><cite><a href="http://www.w3.org/International/articles/inline-bidi-markup/uba-basics">Unicode Bidirectional Algorithm basics</a></cite> is a repackaging of the initial part of &#8220;What you need to know about the bidi algorithm and inline markup&#8221; as a standalone article. It provides a gentle introduction to the behaviour of the Unicode Bidirectional Algorithm, and helps you understand why bidirectional text in Arabic, Hebrew, Thaana, Urdu, etc. behaves the way it does.</p>
				<div class="admin">
					<span class="comments-link"><a href="http://www.w3.org/blog/International/2013/04/29/new-article-unicode-bidirectional-algorithm-basics/#respond" title="Comment on New article: Unicode Bidirectional Algorithm basics">Leave a comment</a></span>
									</div>			
									<div class="cats">
						Tags: <strong><a href="http://www.w3.org/blog/International/tag/article-uba-basics/" rel="tag">article-uba-basics</a></strong>
					</div>
								<div class="cats">Categories: <strong><a href="http://www.w3.org/blog/International/category/articles/" rel="category tag">Articles</a>, <a href="http://www.w3.org/blog/International/category/highlight/" rel="category tag">Highlight</a>, <a href="http://www.w3.org/blog/International/category/new-resource/" rel="category tag">New resource</a>, <a href="http://www.w3.org/blog/International/category/w3cwebarchitecture/" rel="category tag">w3cWebArchitecture</a>, <a href="http://www.w3.org/blog/International/category/w3cwebdesign/" rel="category tag">w3cWebDesign</a>, <a href="http://www.w3.org/blog/International/category/w3cwebofdevices/" rel="category tag">w3cWebOfDevices</a>, <a href="http://www.w3.org/blog/International/category/w3cwebservices/" rel="category tag">w3cWebServices</a>, <a href="http://www.w3.org/blog/International/category/w3cwebuseragents/" rel="category tag">w3cWebUserAgents</a>, <a href="http://www.w3.org/blog/International/category/w3cxmlcore/" rel="category tag">w3cXMLCore</a></strong></div>			</div>
